cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.CV 

This paper involves the application of deep reinforcement learning in robotics, specifically in the context of human-robot interaction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the model using subjective measures, indicating that it could belong to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The use of simulation and perceptual studies suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
